body.description: Make organization fun and easy with the BIC Brite Liner Highlighters Assorted Colors. These highlighters have a chisel tip for broad highlighting or fine underlining, making them perfect for highlighting school or office documents. BIC's highlighter markers use translucent ink to emphasize what's important on the page without obscuring the text below. Reliable and long-lasting, each BIC Brite Liner highlighter writes for up to eight hours without a cap and does not dry out, so you can work with confidence. The convenient pen-shaped design lets you easily grip and comfortably use the highlighters to organize your notes or underline passages in textbooks, notebooks and documents. Looking for classic highlighters for journals or assorted color marker sets for adults? BIC Brite Liner Multicolor Highlighters add a fun pop of flair to your art, office or school supplies. Each pack contains five chisel tip highlighter markers in the following assorted colors: yellow, pink, blue, green and orange. BIC highlighters are ACMI-approved for a high-quality, safe product you can trust. Whether you're emphasizing text or just feel like getting creative, choose BIC Brite Liner Highlighters.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Super-Bright, Fluorescent Ink Available in five super-bright colors yellow, pink, orange, green, and blue BIC Brite Liner Highlighters allow you to easily color-code your notes and documents. The vivid fluorescent inks stand out on the page without obscuring the text underneath. Versatile, Firm Chisel Tip Each BIC Brite Liner Highlighter features a reliable chisel tip that creates both thick and thin lines with ease. You’ll be able to toggle between broad highlighting and fine underlining with just a twist of the wrist. Resists Drying Out BIC Brite Liner Highlighters won't dry out* when the cap is left off for up to eight hours, so you can use them for extended periods of time without having to switch to another highlighter. *when the cap is left off up to 8 hours.

BIC is also part of the global effort to promote access to education and proudly supports hundreds of philanthropic organizations to help ensure quality education for all.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A bright choice for highlighting!
reviews.reviewText: The Bic Brite Liner is my go-to highlighter because it works well, is easy to hold, affordably priced, and the colors are really nice. The pen-style body with a pocket clip makes these highlighters very easy to put in a backpack or pocket, and also lets you easily store them in a pen cup. While Bic labels these highlighters as "fluorescent", it seems like only the yellow highlighter is the usual in-your-face fluorescent shade; but even then it's not bad. The other colors are more subdued compared to other fluorescent highlighters, but that's actually fine by me. Pink and blue are a bit pastel-like but still easy to read through. The orange shade is one of my favorites; it's a deeper orange than is typical for highlighters, but it's still very vibrant and easy to see through. Bic's green is dark and unfortunately doesn't work too well for actual highlighting, but you can use it for underlining; and ditto for the purple one. Overall, though, these are very good little highlighters, and they are another shining example of Bic providing a product that performs a lot better than the low price would suggest.
